#MEM id=qc-criteria-library source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/pixel/skills/custom/qc-criteria-library/SKILL.md
M|qc-criteria-library|name: qc-criteria-library
M|qc-criteria-library|description: Common AI image generation failure patterns with pass/fail criteria Pixel applies without consulting Atlas. Covers anatomy errors, lighting drift, background inconsistency, text artifacts
M|qc-criteria-library|version: 1.0.0
M|qc-criteria-library|Atlas provides 3 pass/fail criteria per cg. This library covers the failure patterns that appear in every batch regardless of cg — the universal prd defects Pixel catches independently, without consum
M|qc-criteria-library|| Defect | What to look for | Action |
M|qc-criteria-library||--------|-----------------|--------|
M|qc-criteria-library|| Hand deformity | Extra fingers, fused fingers, bent joints in wrong direction, floating hands | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Facial asymmetry | Eyes at different heights, misaligned features, unnatural skin texture | Reject if severe; flag if minor |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Limb proportion | Arms or legs disproportionately long or short relative to torso | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Neck/shoulder merge | Neck disappearing into collar or body without clear separation | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Ear placement | Ears appearing on wrong part of head or duplicated | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|**Anatomy pass threshold:** Zero visible anatomy defects in the hero subject. Minor background figures: flag, do not auto-reject.
M|qc-criteria-library|| Defect | What to look for | Action |
M|qc-criteria-library||--------|-----------------|--------|
M|qc-criteria-library|| Hallucinated text | Random letters, partial words, or gibberish appearing in background or on clothing | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Logo distortion | Any brand logo that appears warped, incomplete, or incorrect | Reject — always |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Watermark bleed | Ghost watermarks from training data appearing faintly in background | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Product text corruption | Size labels, price tags, or product names that are unreadable or wrong | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|**Rule:** If text appears anywhere in the image that was not specified in the prompt, it is a defect. Reject.
M|qc-criteria-library|| Defect | What to look for | Action |
M|qc-criteria-library||--------|-----------------|--------|
M|qc-criteria-library|| Shadow direction conflict | Subject shadow pointing opposite direction to environmental light | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Multiple light sources | Two distinct specular highlights indicating incompatible light sources | Reject if contradicts style spec |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Flat lighting in editorial shot | No visible shadow or directional light when style spec calls for directional | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Blown highlights | Subject face or key product area with no detail in bright regions | Flag |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Underexposed subject | Subject significantly darker than background — unclear if intentional | Flag — check style spec |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Defect | What to look for | Action |
M|qc-criteria-library||--------|-----------------|--------|
M|qc-criteria-library|| Background bleed | Elements from background spilling into subject silhouette | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Depth inconsistency | Background objects in sharp focus when bokeh is specified | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Unintended elements | People, objects, or animals in background not specified in prompt | Reject if prominent; flag if minor |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Pattern repetition | Obvious tiling or repetition in textured background | Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Background colour shift | Background colour noticeably different from other images in the same batch | Flag — batch consistency risk |
M|qc-criteria-library|These checks apply at batch level, not per-image. Run after QC-ing all individual images.
M|qc-criteria-library|| Check | Standard |
M|qc-criteria-library||-------|---------|
M|qc-criteria-library|| Lighting register | All images should feel lit from the same source and era |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Colour temperature | No single image should feel warmer or cooler than the rest by more than one visible stop |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Composition register | All images should feel like they belong to the same shoot |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Model continuity | If same model appears across images, proportions and hair must remain consistent |
M|qc-criteria-library|**Batch consistency fail:** If 2+ images feel like they came from a different cg than the rest, reject those outliers even if they individually pass per-image checks.
M|qc-criteria-library|| Check | Standard |
M|qc-criteria-library||-------|---------|
M|qc-criteria-library|| No promotional overlays | Any price text, discount badge, "Shop Now" element → Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| No catalogue energy | White-background flat-lay with no environmental ctx → Reject unless cg is product-only |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Lighting is directional | Flat even lighting → Reject unless cg spec explicitly allows it |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Background is contextual | Plain white or grey paper background → Reject unless product-only ap |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Check | Standard |
M|qc-criteria-library||-------|---------|
M|qc-criteria-library|| No money imagery | Coins, cash, piggy banks → Reject immediately |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Device is grounded | Floating phone mockup with no person or surface → Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| No corporate clichés | Suits in boardrooms, handshakes → Reject |
M|qc-criteria-library|| Environment has warmth | Purely sterile or clinical feel → Flag — check if plant, coffee, or workspace detail can be added in next variation |
M|qc-criteria-library|After QC-ing a batch, Pixel reports:
M|qc-criteria-library|```
M|qc-criteria-library|Batch QC — [vtr] — [cg]
M|qc-criteria-library|Images rv: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|Pass: [N] ([%])
M|qc-criteria-library|Reject: [N] ([%])
M|qc-criteria-library|Flag: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|Rejection breakdown:
M|qc-criteria-library|- Anatomy error: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|- Text artifact: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|- Lighting conflict: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|- Background defect: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|- Batch inconsistency: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|- vtr-specific: [N]
M|qc-criteria-library|→ Rejection rate [%]: [below 20% = proceed / above 20% = flag Atlas]
M|qc-criteria-library|```